29#include <ar.h>
30#include <libelf.h>
31
32#include "_libelf.h"
33
34__RCSID("$NetBSD: elf_rand.c,v 1.3 2016/02/20 02:43:42 christos Exp $");
35ELFTC_VCSID("Id: elf_rand.c 3174 2015-03-27 17:13:41Z emaste ");
36
37off_t
38elf_rand(Elf *ar, off_t offset)
39{
40 struct ar_hdr *arh;
41
42 if (ar == NULL || ar->e_kind != ELF_K_AR ||
43 (offset & 1) || offset < SARMAG ||
44 (size_t) offset + sizeof(struct ar_hdr) >= ar->e_rawsize) {
45 LIBELF_SET_ERROR(ARGUMENT, 0);
46 return 0;
47 }
48
49 arh = (struct ar_hdr *) (ar->e_rawfile + offset);
50
51 /* a too simple sanity check */
52 if (arh->ar_fmag[0] != '`' || arh->ar_fmag[1] != '\n') {
53 LIBELF_SET_ERROR(ARCHIVE, 0);
54 return 0;
55 }
56
57 ar->e_u.e_ar.e_next = offset;
58
59 return (offset);
60}
